13:18.960 --> 13:21.849
but I've had a little
legal trouble of my own,

13:21.900 --> 13:22.992
and I've been suspended

13:23.030 --> 13:24.497
from practicing law
for six months.

13:24.530 --> 13:26.998
You?

13:27.040 --> 13:28.291
Really?

13:28.340 --> 13:30.035
What happened?

13:30.070 --> 13:31.401
I cut some corners.

13:31.440 --> 13:32.168
I'm a corner-cutter.

13:32.210 --> 13:34.906
Ah, so this
is a 12-step program?

13:34.940 --> 13:37.443
Yes, step three,
admitting my faults.

13:37.480 --> 13:40.278
