to other fine lawyers here,

13:40.320 --> 13:42.880
so you probably want
to ask Julius Cain

13:42.920 --> 13:45.218
whether he's crazy
to go after hockey.

13:45.250 --> 13:46.888
And who's the other lavwer?
What?

13:46.920 --> 13:48.410
