13:48.460 --> 13:50.451
Who's the other lawyer?
Alicia Florrick.

13:50.490 --> 13:53.459
Oh... yes.

13:53.500 --> 13:55.923
Alicia. How is she doing?

13:55.960 --> 13:57.188
Good.

13:57.230 --> 13:58.390
Good.

13:58.430 --> 14:01.593
I'm so glad for her.

14:03.110 --> 14:05.260
Well...

14:05.310 --> 14:07.870
it was good seeing you, Will.

14:08.910 --> 14:11.071
You're looking good.

14:11.110 --> 14:12.919
Thank you.
You are, too.

14:12.950 --> 14:14.941
Good luck
with your other nine steps.

14:16.550 --> 14:18.313
The league ended up suspending
Cameron Raker

14:18.350 --> 14:19.487
for the rest of the season,

14:19.520 --> 14:22.011
so the state's attorney
at the time,

14:22.060 --> 14:23.357
Peter Florrick,

14:23.390 --> 14:25.620
thought it wasn't
worth pursuing.

14:25.660 --> 14:27.389
But what was
the charge gonna be?

14:27.430 --> 14:29.352
I mean, why was
this treated different

14:29.400 --> 14:31.163
than any other fight on the ice?

14:31.200 --> 14:34.499
Well, the concussion was severe,
and we were looking into it

14:34.540 --> 14:35.962
being a premeditated hit.

14:36.000 --> 14:37.467
Raker targeted our client?

14:37.510 --> 14:39.398
The whole team targeted
your client.

14:39.440 --> 14:43.001
Any chance I could see the
investigative report on that?

14:43.050 --> 14:45.245
Or just a peek?

14:45.280 --> 14:49.148
Funny that you've been sent here
and not Kalinda.

14:49.180 --> 14:51.284
I volunteered.

14:51.320 --> 14:53.982
(chuckles)
Really?

14:56.090 --> 14:58.081
Why?

14:58.130 --> 14:59.552
I don't know.

15:01.400 --> 15:04.289
How are you doing?

15:04.330 --> 15:08.266
Well, I'm not
in the deputy's office.

15:08.300 --> 15:11.007
Yes, I, um... I wasn't
gonna say anything.

15:11.040 --> 15:12.359
Things have changed.

15:12.410 --> 15:14.378
Self-inflicted wound.

15:14.410 --> 15:16.378
Are you safe?

15:16.410 --> 15:19.402
Nobody's told me otherwise,

15:19.450 --> 15:22.010
and that usually means no.

15:22.050 --> 15:25.110
Thank you.

15:25.150 --> 15:26.082
Cameron Raker.

15:26.120 --> 15:28.486
I am a professional
ice hockey left-winger.

15:28.520 --> 15:30.329
