term to bias these proceedings.

15:34.660 --> 15:36.696
I don't understand;
what's the bias?

15:36.730 --> 15:38.129
Well, an enforcer

15:38.170 --> 15:40.138
is someone on a hockey
team who responds

15:40.170 --> 15:42.161
to supposedly dirty plays
from the opposing team

15:42.200 --> 15:44.134
by attacking aggressively...

15:44.170 --> 15:46.559
