15:53.080 --> 15:54.342
Mr. Raker,

15:54.380 --> 15:56.075
what is the official title
for your p05ition?

15:56.120 --> 15:57.348
RAKER:
Uh, left wing.

15:57.390 --> 15:59.688
Okay, that's what we'll
call it from now on.

15:59.720 --> 16:01.585
Left wing.
And I...

16:01.620 --> 16:04.123
Um...

16:04.160 --> 16:06.458
Mr. Raker...

16:06.490 --> 16:08.424
in your capacity
as a left-winger,

16:08.460 --> 16:10.098
did your coach ever ask you

16:10.130 --> 16:12.519
