16:28.280 --> 16:29.474
Yeah.
I'm sorry,

16:29.520 --> 16:31.044
I've got to come closer;
I can't see.

16:31.090 --> 16:32.978
Oh, certainly, Your Honor.

16:36.160 --> 16:37.582
And who is that

16:37.630 --> 16:38.779
