your star player?

16:38.830 --> 16:41.048
Him.

16:41.100 --> 16:43.125
ANNOUNCER:
Oh, devastating hit

16:43.170 --> 16:45.058
by Duverney on Lund.

16:45.100 --> 16:46.397
And the best man on the ice

16:46.430 --> 16:47.397
is taken down by a fourth-liner.

16:47.440 --> 16:50.603
Was your team outraged
by this hit, Mr. Raker?

16:50.640 --> 16:52.631
