16:52.670 --> 16:54.535
We were concerned.

16:54.580 --> 16:55.808
Lund is pretty important to us.

16:55.840 --> 16:58.547
But did you see
this postgame interview?

16:58.580 --> 17:02.141
You hit us like that,
it's not over.

17:02.180 --> 17:04.148
We've got your number, Duverney.

17:04.190 --> 17:06.078
We'll see you in February.

17:06.120 --> 17:07.610
RAKER:
Nope, didn't see it.

17:07.660 --> 17:09.685
