to meet up with Canning.

18:24.700 --> 18:26.691
Obviously, I can't comment.

18:26.730 --> 18:28.334
I will keep you
in the loop.

18:28.370 --> 18:29.735
Not at my urging.

18:29.770 --> 18:31.635
Bye.

18:31.670 --> 18:34.275
Okay, let me know
when you find out more.

18:34.310 --> 18:35.572
Mm-hmm.

18:35.610 --> 18:37.646
(beep)

18:37.680 --> 18:40.513
Back to our old
ways, are we?

18:40.550 --> 18:42.177
And what ways
might those be?

18:42.220 --> 18:44.745
Paying off our
neurological expert.

18:46.390 --> 18:47.618
Are you happy

18:47.660 --> 18:49.184
