18:58.200 --> 18:59.326
Okay.

18:59.370 --> 19:01.588
Here's the problem.

19:01.640 --> 19:04.359
I see how we treat
lawyers who are poached.

19:04.410 --> 19:06.207
They're the first
ones out the door.

19:06.240 --> 19:07.776
They're the ones
we don't trust,

19:07.810 --> 19:10.699
and that is why I
will not be poached.

19:10.750 --> 19:13.947
The problem at
Lockhart & Gardner is they
treat it like a family.

19:13.980 --> 19:16.369
They treat loyalty
