19:26.890 --> 19:28.357
Let me make you an offer.

19:28.400 --> 19:30.789
No.

19:30.830 --> 19:32.969
Afraid Mommy and Daddy
at Lockhart & Gardner

19:33.000 --> 19:34.638
might get upset?

19:34.670 --> 19:36.490
I'll see you in court.

19:36.540 --> 19:38.508
See you in court.

19:38.540 --> 19:39.859
And, Dr. Rubich,
as the team doctor,

19:39.910 --> 19:41.969
