20:09.370 --> 20:10.667
CANNING:
Dr. Rubich,

20:10.710 --> 20:12.666
what's a baseline test?

20:12.710 --> 20:15.634
It's a neuro-psychological
test we run on players

20:15.680 --> 20:17.375
before the start
of the season.

20:17.410 --> 20:20.675
