20:26.450 --> 20:27.815
after he was knocked down
by Cameron Raker?

20:27.860 --> 20:28.610
Yes, and the results

20:28.660 --> 20:30.821
were identical
with the baseline.

20:30.860 --> 20:32.782
There were no signs
of brain trauma.

20:32.830 --> 20:34.627
So, in other words,
you did your job?

20:34.660 --> 20:35.695
(chuckles)
Yes.

20:35.730 --> 20:37.266
Thank you, Doctor.

20:37.300 --> 20:39.495
We need our neurologist.

20:39.530 --> 20:42.636
Kalinda thinks he'll meet
with Canning after court.

